You have exceeded your premium request allowance. We have automatically switched you to GPT-4.1 which is included with your plan. [Enable additional paid premium requests](command:chat.enablePremiumOverages) to continue using premium models.```seqdiag
actor User
boundary ProductPage
control ProductController
participant ":ProductService" as Service
participant ":ProductModel" as Model
database Database

User->ProductPage: 1. Open products list page
activate ProductPage
activate User
ProductPage->ProductController: 2. GET /products
activate ProductController

ProductController->Service: 5. Process product list retrieval
activate Service

alt Products not found
    Service->Model: 6.1 Fetch products
    activate Model
    Model->Database: 6.1.1 SELECT products (with filters/paging)
    activate Database
    Database-->Model: 6.1.2 Result set (empty)
    deactivate Database
    Model-->Service: 6.1.3 Return list (empty)
    deactivate Model
    Service-->ProductController: 6.1.4 Return empty result
    ProductController-->ProductPage: 6.1.5 Return 200 OK + empty list/message
    ProductPage-->User: 6.1.6 Show "No products available"
else Products found
    Service->Model: 6.2 Fetch products
    activate Model
    Model->Database: 6.2.1 SELECT products
    activate Database
    Database-->Model: 6.2.2 Result set (list)
    deactivate Database
    Model-->Service: 6.2.3 Return products list
    deactivate Model
    Service-->ProductController: 6.2.4 Return ProductListResponse
    deactivate Service
    ProductController-->ProductPage: 6.2.5 Return 200 OK + products data
    ProductPage->ProductPage: 6.2.6 Render products list
end

ProductPage-->User: 7. Display page content (list or empty state)
deactivate ProductPage
deactivate User
```